#Name: data_exfil_observed_via_ftp
#Description: This alert looks for .zip files being sent via ftp.
#Definition
Custom query: event.dataset : zeek.ftp and event.action : STOR and zeek.ftp.arg : *.zip
Rule Type: Query
Timeline template: None
Suppress alerts by: Destination.ip
Suppress alerts for: 5m
If a suppression field is missing: Suppress and group alerts for events with missing fields
#Schedule
Runs every: 5m
Additional look-back time: 5m